item.title: CVE-2023-39155|2024-08-02T18:02:06.654Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20chef%20identity%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Chef Identity Plugin 2.0.3 and earlier does not mask the user.pem key form field, increasing the potential for attackers to observe and capture it.
